                  "text": "Pillars 1 / 2 / 5 / 6 — all aligned for action post-DD. P1 (technical) __Demand-Driven EPSU confirmed__ on both daily and weekly charts; P2 (paradigm) supportive macro; P5 (sell-side) consensus 22% below modal case with three identifiable revision catalysts; P6 (upside) implied IRR 24% blended, adding 6-7% optionality value via KPOs.",
